{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究并了解</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光折射时的特点。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">光从一种介质斜射入另一种介质时，会发生折射现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">激光笔、水槽</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">玻璃砖等</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.提出问题</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光从空气进入</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水中或玻璃以后传播方向是否发生了偏折</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">？向哪个</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方向</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">偏折</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">？</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.设计实验和进行实验</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">让一束光从空气以</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同的角度射入水中</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">或</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">玻璃</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察光束在空气中和水中的</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">径</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">迹。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.分析与论证</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据上述实验的现象，试着总结光折射的规律。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.折射光线与入射光线和法线在同一平面内。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.折射光线与入射光线分居法线两侧。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.当光从空气斜射入水或玻璃时，折射角小于入射角。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.当光从水或玻璃中斜射入空气时，折射角大于入射角。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.当入射角增大时，折射角也随着增大</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发生光的折射现象时会同时存在光的反射现象。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}